data.description: This gorgeous home sits on just over an acre with a beautifully landscaped front yard and is a must SEE! It offers over 2,700 sq ft of living space with 2100+ sq ft in the main home and an additional 500+ sq ft in the pool house. This home is family ready with lots of space including 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, updated kitchen and lots of storage. The outdoor entertainment area is breathtaking with the spacious back patio, inground heated pool, hot tub, firepit & large fenced in backyard. All appliances except washer/dryer are included, even pool house appliances. House and pool house both have BRAND NEW roof.
